00_cleaner.ipynb: A document cleaner written in Python to remove stopwords and unwanted sign. Besides you can choose if you like to filter all words, adjectives, nouns or verbs.

millercenter_scraper.ipynb: A small web scraping algorithm written in Python that got the collection of texts for both Bush and Obama.


This file contains trump/biden/obama/bush speeches and "mein kampf" in english.
sources:
  Trump + Biden:
  https://www.rev.com/blog/transcripts/all-transcripts

  Bush:
  https://millercenter.org/the-presidency/presidential-speeches => select George W. Bush

  Obama:
  https://millercenter.org/the-presidency/presidential-speeches => select Barack Obama

  Mein Kampf:
  https://archive.org/details/mein-kampf-stalag-edition
